nodes.text: A mission was launched by the Jedi Order to infiltrate and destroy the Starcrusher, a powerful Separatist warship capable of destroying multiple Republic Star Destroyers. A Jedi strike team, comprised of Mace Windu, Ki-Adi-Mundi, Obi-Wan Kenobi, Jyl Somtay, and Ahsoka Tano, ultimately succeeded in destroying the warship, with assistance from Jedi Knight Anakin Skywalker.
